extendedInfo.description: A lightweight live Houston traffic info for Houston's commuters. Faster than Web/Google Maps!FEATURES:- Traffic CAMS. Yes!- Traffic Maps- Incidents- Highway InfoAll traffic info is provided by Houston TranStar.PS: I REALLY APPRECIATE EVERYONE'S FEEDBACKS - I am working on updates!

reviews.title: Better than nothing...
reviews.comment: Not too shabby. Would be better of it fit my screen properly or had the ability to report incidents.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Easily my favorite and most recommended app. Extremely useful and highly practical. Thanks for developing this.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Excellent App
reviews.comment: Very easy to use, especially compared to trying to use the Transtar website on phone\'s browser! I would like to make a suggestion: make the street traffic map one of the choices. I drive Richmond and Westheimer everyday and would really appreciate this addition. (T-Mobile Samsung Exhibit II)
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: THIS IS A FABULOUS APP!!! I love, love, LOVE IT!!!! I highly reccommend it for everyone! The live camera photos- top info as you\'re on the road.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Worked great until 4.3...
reviews.comment: Really like this app. Use it every time I\'m about to jump in the car. However, I updated my Android to 4.3 Jelly Bean today, and the maps won\'t load! Is anybody else having this issue?
reviews.author: Patrick Garrett

reviews.comment: So awesome! The live street views are helpful even though Houston traffic always sucks. Please add more traffic cams! DroidMoto
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Great!
reviews.comment: I use it every day. It\'s simple and has just what I need on my way out the door.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: This is a good app, saves time over going to sites, but the cameras will make this a 5 star app!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Superb program, would be 5 star if it allowed zoom and hide settings to view complete cam feed.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Too slow
reviews.comment: Takes way too long to post incident.  Wrecks are already cleared by the time they\'re posted.  Very frustrating.  Google maps with traffic layer is much more reliable.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Galaxy s3 AT&T
reviews.comment: Takes too long to load and sometimes doesn\'t load at all. Had the same problem with my HTC on Sprint
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Just like TranStar
reviews.comment: Must-have in Houston traffic, more accurate real-time than Google Maps.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Moving back to Houston next week! This will DEFINITELY be coming in handy for my new husband!! :)
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Best application ever! Incredibly useful! Extremely accurate! I am sooo impressed! Amazing application!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Nice, fairly accurate. Cam pics directionally ambiguous. Good, functional app.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Needs update
reviews.comment: Doesn\'t utilize bigger screen resolutions. West/South beltway cams missing. Dead app. No update in years. Literally. Good app though.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Almostperfect! It would be great if I could zoom in and some of the larger \"small\"roads (hwy 6, 1960, 90, etc) like you can on the website
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Love this App
reviews.comment: I have this on my phone. Would love to see it have a wide screen for my Touchpad
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.comment: Awesome app! Now I don\'t get stuck in traffic everyday!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Much faster than going to transtar website.
reviews.comment: My only suggestion is to have a full map which we can scroll around with instead of the smaller \"area\" maps.
